      "imputation_interpretation": "All 70 period-2 (2020-22) education observations are forward-filled from a frozen 2017 anchor (100.0% of period-2, 43.5% of total N=161). The within-SD of 0.4135 years is an artifact of comparing a 2015-19 average against a single 2017 endpoint, not genuine educational change."
